text_en:
Perfect timing.
I will show you
something interesting.{END}

Those who undergo bio-remodeling
must possess superior intellect
and physical strength.　{END}

It was wrong from the start
to seek those qualities
in imperfect humans.{END}

Then all we need do
is create bodies
with perfect qualities.{END}

If this experiment succeeds,
we will no longer need
to capture humans as base bodies.{END}

We need only inject
the bio-remodeling virus
into all of these perfect bodies.{END}
